%sort false_imp_lookupMethod {_ false} {_ lookupMethod MR1 M (method D0 M (%the (bexp DS) BE2))} {_ lookupMethod MR1 M (method C0 M (%the (bexp CS) BE3))} %.
%mode {%in MR1 methodTable} {%in M methodName} {%in N1 nat} {%in DS cnlist N1} {%in D0 className} {%in BE2 bexp DS} {%in N2 nat} {%in CS cnlist N2} {%in C0 className} {%out BE3 bexp CS} {%in F false} {%in LM1 lookupMethod MR1 M (method D0 M BE2)} {%out LM2 lookupMethod MR1 M (method C0 M BE3)} false_imp_lookupMethod F LM1 LM2 %.
%worlds (var) (false_imp_lookupMethod F L M) %.
%total F (false_imp_lookupMethod F L M) %.
%% mtype is unique, so DS = CS (and same length!) and D0 = C0
%sort mtype_unique {_ mtype CT M C DS D0} {_ mtype CT M C CS C0} {_ lookupMethod MR1 M (method D0 M (%the (bexp DS) BE2))} {_ lookupMethod MR1 M (method C0 M (%the (bexp CS) BE3))} %.
